title: Calling You Home
lyrics:
In the dark
I'm losing my way
I need your lie
I know it's hard
But baby don't fade
It's worth the fight



Cause it's all my heart can take

[?] my mistakes

Scared and it's too late

So please



Don't say it's the end of the story

Don't say it's the end of the road

Cause as long as you are holding me

I'll always be calling you home

Don't know if it is the end for me

But I don't [?]

Cause as long as you are holding me

I'll always be calling you home
